title: Lady Gaga: I feel like myself doing 'American Horror Story: Hotel'
text:
*London:* Pop star Lady Gaga has opened up about her experience of appearing on 'American Horror Story: Hotel', saying that she felt more herself.*Lady Gaga*
The 'Born This Way' singer plays The Countess Elizabeth in the show's fifth season, reported Digital Spy.
